[1-10] The man walks towards the camera with one hand on his leg, limping. As the camera switches, another woman in a black dress appears in the picture, sitting on the steps by the fountain with a brown handbag in her hand. The man stops in front of the woman and turns to look at the woman in the khaki dress. The woman smiles and gets up. The woman in the black dress slings her bag over her shoulder, and the man turns and walks back.
